        },
        "remediation": "Customers are advised to refer to <A HREF=\"https://portal.msrc.microsoft.com/en-US/security-guidance/advisory/ADV180018\" TARGET=\"_blank\">ADV180018</A> for more details pertaining to this vulnerability.<P>",
        "impact": "An attacker who has successfully exploited L1TF may be able to read privileged data across trust boundaries. In shared resource environments (such that exist in some cloud services configurations), this vulnerability could allow one virtual machine to improperly access information from another. An attacker would need prior access to the system or the ability to run code on the system to leverage this vulnerability. <P>",
