          "threat": "Microsoft releases the security update for Internet Explorer December 2019<P>\nThe KB Articles associated with the update:<BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530734\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530734</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530714\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530714</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530691\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530691</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530702\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530702</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530677\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530677</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530689\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530689</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530715\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530715</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530684\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530684</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530717\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530717</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530695\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530695</A><BR>\n<A HREF=\"https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4530681\" TARGET=\"_blank\">KB4530681</A><BR>\n<P>QID Detection Logic:Authenticated<BR>\nThis QID checks for the file version of ntoskrnl.exe for Windows 10 1809, Windows 10 1803 and Windows Server 2019 1809 (i.e. KB4530715) , because Mshtml.dll was not updated for these builds. For the rest we check for Mshtml.dll.\n<P>The following versions with their corresponding KBs are verified:<BR>\nKB4530734 - 11.0.9600.19572<BR>\nKB4530714 - 11.0.16299.1565<BR>\nKB4530691 - 10.0.9200.22931<BR>\nKB4530702 - 11.0.9600.19572<BR>\nKB4530677 - 10.0.9200.22931 , 11.0.9600.19572 , 9.0.8112.21392<BR>\nKB4530689 - 11.0.14393.3383<BR>\nKB4530715 - 10.0.17763.914<BR>\nKB4530684 - 11.0.18362.535<BR>\nKB4530695 - 9.0.8112.21392<BR>\nKB4530681 - 11.0.10240.18427<BR>\n",
